attributes.name: Download S3 Files In Multiple Parts

fields.name: v_task_system_id
fields.expression:
SUBSTR(
  __OtherResponseHeaders__,
  INSTR(__OtherResponseHeaders__, '/tasks/') + LENGTH('/tasks/'),
  INSTR(__OtherResponseHeaders__, '#_#', INSTR(__OtherResponseHeaders__, '/tasks/')) 
    - (INSTR(__OtherResponseHeaders__, '/tasks/') + LENGTH('/tasks/'))
)

fields.name: straight_through_processing_api_data_transferred_to_guidewire_datetime
fields.expression:
TO_DATE(
  SUBSTR(
    __OtherResponseHeaders__,
    INSTR(__OtherResponseHeaders__, 'Date::') + LENGTH('Date::'),
    IIF(
      INSTR(__OtherResponseHeaders__, '#_#', INSTR(__OtherResponseHeaders__, 'Date::')) > 0,
      INSTR(__OtherResponseHeaders__, '#_#', INSTR(__OtherResponseHeaders__, 'Date::'))
        - (INSTR(__OtherResponseHeaders__, 'Date::') + LENGTH('Date::')),
      LENGTH(__OtherResponseHeaders__) - (INSTR(__OtherResponseHeaders__, 'Date::') + LENGTH('Date::'))
    )
  ),
  'DY, DD MON YYYY HH24:MI:SS "GMT"'
)
